<article>

<h1>Professional Cleaning Checklist</h1>

<p>
Professional cleaning services normally follow a checklist to ensure
consistent results.
</p>

<h2>Kitchen</h2>

<ul>
<li>Worktops cleaned</li>
<li>Sinks cleaned</li>
<li>Appliance exteriors wiped</li>
<li>Floors vacuumed and mopped</li>
</ul>

<h2>Bathrooms</h2>

<ul>
<li>Toilet sanitised</li>
<li>Shower and bath cleaned</li>
<li>Sinks and taps cleaned</li>
<li>Mirrors wiped</li>
</ul>

<h2>Living Areas</h2>

<ul>
<li>Dusting surfaces</li>
<li>Vacuuming carpets</li>
<li>Mopping hard floors</li>
</ul>

</article>

